Install
  Install ApacheSolr (e.g. with `brew install solr`)

  Install Scons (e.g. with `brew install scons`)

  Clone http://github.com/polotek/libxmljs.git, 
  run `make libxmljs.node`
  and `npm install .`

  Clone http://github.com/gsf/node-solr.git
  and run `npm install .`



Start ApacheSolr (with Homebrew install):
  solr "`pwd`/solr"
  (Make sure to use an absolute path for the instance dir)
